data.name: lblKeyInfo.Text
data.value:
Select the assignments from the Button, Usage and Key Command drop down lists
Click the Apply button to set the assignments.
Entries in the Usage and Key Command boxes can be made directly from keyboard input (visible keystrokes only, shift, enter, ctrl etc. will not register)
If Hat Switch use is enabled buttons are limited to a maximum of 24 buttons. A warning will appear if the button count exceeds 24 buttons.
